# Why wasm?
speed, smaller footprint, distributed computing
Security: Rigid sandbox, Memory Isolation, Buffer overrun security exploit not possible
rapid Continuous deployment, portable, browser, cloud, IoT
0 downtime deployment, live module version swap without containers

# How to write wasm? Wasm is Polyglott
Emscripten, rust, go, Assemlbyscript, C/C++

> build amazing thing outside the browser

# wasm runtime?
out of browser runtimes
add1.wat        low-level IR code
wasmtime add1.wasm --invoke add 2 2 

# How to build cloud native services in web assembly?
cloud/service health checks
no tight coupling, dynamically bound @runtime
